# Day 2 – Quiz Game 🎯

## What it does
A terminal-based quiz game that asks 5 math questions,
checks your answers, and gives you a final score.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3 (built-in only)

## How to run
python quiz.py

## What I learned
- Functions with parameters
- Conditionals (if/else)
- Lists of tuples
- For loops
- f-strings

## Output
Tells you if you got each question right or wrong,
then prints your final score out of 5.
